OL,3,CResidents patrolling streets as anti-
OL,4,Csocial bike riding becoming 'the norm'
OL,6,FJennie Henry has been to Yarm Road in
OL,7,FStockton, where residents say anti-
OL,8,Fsocial bike riding is getting
OL,9,F'ridiculous'
OL,11,FA local residents' association in
OL,12,FStockton say they are so fed up of
OL,13,Fanti-social bike riding that they have
OL,14,Fset up night time patrols to try and
OL,15,Fdeter this type of behaviour.
OL,17,FPeople living in the Yarm Road area of
OL,18,Fthe town told ITV News that some
OL,19,Friders are terrorising the area, and
OL,20,Fthat the situation is now getting
OL,21,F'ridiculous'.
