OL,4,Csocial bike riding becoming 'the norm'
OL,6,FThe road is one of the busiest routes
OL,7,Finto Stockton, stretching all the way
OL,8,Ffrom Eaglescliffe and Yarm up into the
OL,9,Ftown centre.
OL,11,FResidents say riders often go on the
OL,12,Ffootpath, and this has led to some
OL,13,Fnear-miss occurrences.
OL,15,FTariq Mahmood from the local residents
OL,16,Fassociation said: "We do try to flag
OL,17,Fthese guys down, we do ask them to
OL,18,Fcalm down. I think we're just being
OL,19,Flaughed at and nothing is really being
OL,20,Fdone."
